ItemInfo.name: deviantCell
ItemInfo.value: select aa.cell from (SELECT DIM_NE_UTRANCELL.Uc_Desc cell, ROUND(sum(UP_FLOW), 4) "-446830229" FROM DW_A_RE_ST_XDR_UC_D T, DIM_NE_UTRANCELL WHERE T.uc_id = DIM_NE_UTRANCELL.uc_id AND T.DAY_ID = 20130912 group by DIM_NE_UTRANCELL.Uc_Desc) aa, (SELECT DIM_NE_UTRANCELL.Uc_Desc cell, ROUND(sum(TOTAL_FLOW), 4) "695866332" FROM DW_A_RE_ST_XDR_UC_D T, DIM_NE_UTRANCELL WHERE T.uc_id = DIM_NE_UTRANCELL.uc_id AND T.DAY_ID = 20130912 group by DIM_NE_UTRANCELL.Uc_Desc) bb where aa.cell = bb.cell and aa. "-446830229" >= 0 and bb. "695866332" > 0
